I like Richard Lindley , and I hope he'll see his fifty thousand dollars again . 
I wouldn't have given Corliss thirty cents . 
Why do you think he's a crook ? I don't say that , returned Trumble . 
All I know about him is that he's done some of the finest work to get fifty thousand dollars put in his hands that I ever heard of . 
And all anybody knows about him is that he lived here seventeen years ago , and comes back claiming to know where there's oil in Italy . 
He shows some maps and papers and gets cablegrams signed Moliterno . 
He'll not get a cent if it's sold . 
And he's got Cora Madison so crazy over him that she makes life a hell for poor old Lindley until he puts all he's saved into the bubble . 
The scheme may be all right . 
Not your kind either , retorted the other going to the door . 
She cut me on the street the other day she's quit speaking to me . 
