How far are you going with Do you want me to walk away and leave you ? she asked , suddenly sitting up straight and looking at him with dilating eyes . 
If you want a scene' It's over , he said , more calmly . 
I know now how dangerous the man is . 
Of course you will tell him I said that . 
Not after what you've said . 
I had a foolish idea you could behave well , at least decently . 
Did Corliss tell you that I insulted him in his rooms at the hotel ? You ! She laughed , genuinely . 
I see him letting you ! He did , however . 
By manner and in speech I purposely and deliberately insulted him . 
