I'll try to give you the proper cues if you'll indicate the general nature of the scene , Cora mine . 
She continued to look at him in silence . 
It's very effective , he observed . 
Brings out the figure , too . 
Do forgive me if you're serious , dear lady , but never in my life was I able to take the folded arms business seriously . 
It was used on the stage of all countries so much that I believe most new school actors have dropped it . 
They think it lacks genuineness . 
